---
/**
 * The WIZAG wordmark geometry, defined once per page as an SVG <symbol>.
 *
 * Logo.astro then references it with <use>, so the (large) path data appears
 * a single time in the document instead of once per placement — header,
 * mobile drawer and footer would otherwise repeat ~7.5KB each.
 *
 * Rendered once by BaseLayout at the top of <body>. Any page using
 * <Logo /> outside BaseLayout must include this itself.
 *
 * viewBox is the artwork's measured bounding box, so the mark sits flush to
 * its box with no phantom padding. The wordmark uses currentColor and
 * inherits from wherever the <use> sits; only the accent is fixed to brand
 * orange. The white background plate from the supplied file is dropped — it
 * is not transparent despite the filename and would show as a white box on
 * any non-white ground.
 */
